		<p>The blonde grimaced. "Not much," she admitted. She gave Zee a wistful glance. "I thought, when you kissed someone, it was supposed to feel wonderful."</p>
		<p>Zee thought about that for a bit and mentally tossed a coin.
			<i>All right, here goes. </i>"Perhaps you weren't doing it right."
		</p>
		<p>"What do you mean?"</p>
